Verificando a versao do Docker
docker -v

Verificando se esta funcionando
docker help

Instalando Postgress
docker run --name  database -e POSTGRES_PASSWORD=docker -p 5432:5432 -d postgres

listando os container 
docker ps

parando docker
docker stop database

listando containers
docker ps -a

Iniciando o docker
docker start database

docker log
docker logs database